Name: Trapped with Jester
About the game: About this game: Your head aches. Your memory is in shambles. You hear the clip-clop of a horse's careful steps. You feel shaking around you... and a pair of eyes watching you. You are awakened by a voice. An unfamiliar face. Where are you? Who are you? Why are you here...? ... AND WHY WON'T THAT ANNOYING STRANGER SHUT UP?! Features: -1000 Words -4 Main endings + 2 Alternate endings (Total of 6 endings) -Original Artwork -Fully-Voiced
